{"tid":5804,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩PS4耳機好用？","createTime":"2016-11-27T05:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T15:15:03.000Z","uid":19572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f87dd20c0532b842406923d1b96b92b19333ef3","tid":5804,"uid":19572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:27:08.000Z","msg":"好似turtle beach同astro console耳機最出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要想搵無線耳機，有時淨係想party吹水都方便<br />\n暫時睇岩520p/elite800/A40+mix amp/A50<br />\n因為價錢都並幾遠，有冇用過既巴打分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e46a415793c2390302d8813222ea03324b48fc","tid":5804,"uid":23964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:54:20.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d26bd1e3214df1558c564529783e0725962a17da","tid":5804,"uid":22926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:41:40.000Z","msg":"用緊a50一年了<br />\n好滿意<br />\n但好似有隻用藍牙<br />\n可聽埋電話"},{"pid":"26a70671cf3b9a05441a66188cca162ee2131db3","tid":5804,"uid":22658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"其實sony自己果隻都好用"},{"pid":"7def4cab143d6dc706e295e726c5950eb9b325cf","tid":5804,"uid":2874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:17:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實sony自己果隻都好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冬天就正，夏天出晒汗，玩3-4個鐘開始feel到耳仔痛"},{"pid":"092d4841bc8be4ff626d2894fd9bdbcde2de6e08","tid":5804,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實sony自己果隻都好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk係口.net/upload/2016/11/27/190036_2c977171d7c856e4a64334442dc45725.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk%E4%BF%82%E5%8F%A3.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F190036_2c977171d7c856e4a64334442dc45725.jpg&h=5234c62a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪呢隻？我自己用緊 覺得幾好，有粒制可以調game音量大小（但人聲唔變） 同friend吹水打機幾好用"},{"pid":"e2a8f6014687ef4c7605e69085d145be206d1754","tid":5804,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實sony自己果隻都好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/190036_2c977171d7c856e4a64334442dc45725.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F190036_2c977171d7c856e4a64334442dc45725.jpg&h=06b37f42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪呢隻？我自己用緊 覺得幾好，有粒制可以調game音量大小（但人聲唔變） 同friend吹水打機幾好用</blockquote>"},{"pid":"43345981502d8d0018666725e4d486c7ff471ba4","tid":5804,"uid":19572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實sony自己果隻都好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冬天就正，夏天出晒汗，玩3-4個鐘開始feel到耳仔痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSomy 原廠有用，做工好差，耳罩唔係可換式，用幾個月甩皮，而且粒電好短"},{"pid":"5df5225d10dc0ec3a621657730578c97af1ed8e0","tid":5804,"uid":19572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊a50一年了<br />\n好滿意<br />\n但好似有隻用藍牙<br />\n可聽埋電話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打用A50 gen2<br />\n佢新出左gen3<br />\n想買，但二千幾真係有d貴<br />\n所以木睇下有冇ching用過平價model<br />\n<br />\n藍牙個隻應該係A38?<br />\n個隻console好似用唔到"},{"pid":"167c68618a8c2f20ddeb08133c916333950bea66","tid":5804,"uid":922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實sony自己果隻都好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冬天就正，夏天出晒汗，玩3-4個鐘開始feel到耳仔痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSomy 原廠有用，做工好差，耳罩唔係可換式，<span style=\"color: red;\">用幾個月甩皮</span>，而且粒電好短</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a724e896937ec688d19c2df6082cbd7551e49802","tid":5804,"uid":214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:50:51.000Z","msg":"放ps4 7.1耳機 有興趣pm 使用不超過3粒鐘"},{"pid":"2f7a0016bd555d55f333a6224d34c87218f703c8","tid":5804,"uid":19572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放ps4 7.1耳機 有興趣pm 使用不超過3粒鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我用過，甩皮太勁，已經掉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感謝好意，但不了"},{"pid":"95fd323a162f5c62a2473ba6cae86969789a138d","tid":5804,"uid":22926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊a50一年了<br />\n好滿意<br />\n但好似有隻用藍牙<br />\n可聽埋電話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打用A50 gen2<br />\n佢新出左gen3<br />\n想買，但二千幾真係有d貴<br />\n所以木睇下有冇ching用過平價model<br />\n<br />\n藍牙個隻應該係A38?<br />\n個隻console好似用唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n耳機依啲始終一分一分貨<br />\n貴買平用<br />\n條數就返黎<br />\nA50比起原裝Sony個聲音辨位好好多<br />\n音質更加無得比啦<br />\n最緊要係個a50電腦,Xbox one都用得"},{"pid":"16b65119a2b4d4419c75a9401c58fba16ab2ec36","tid":5804,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"用過sony ps4果隻 a50 隻耳仔唔太岩形狀 一開始好舒服 兩三個鐘之後就好痛"},{"pid":"3594ae91086f4b3391682e43661dc747aedd0819","tid":5804,"uid":28298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:45:36.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"09d6af9cd9db04ed7945269bbb74f3251de0c0b7","tid":5804,"uid":22658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實sony自己果隻都好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冬天就正，夏天出晒汗，玩3-4個鐘開始feel到耳仔痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSomy 原廠有用，做工好差，耳罩唔係可換式，用幾個月甩皮，而且粒電好短</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咁誇張？我用左成年都未甩皮喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 粒電連續6個鐘左右"},{"pid":"959c4b1ceb211dd272384c17fe4b1a5853d84de0","tid":5804,"uid":29738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"elite800<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b089df1e3ae0e6cbe55f7a5526a0d28cacf86068","tid":5804,"uid":3793